You will need...

The main package includes the GForm executable, installer scripts and some examples on how to use GForm.

Download the complete distribution package.
Download the <a href="https://github.com/BruceSteers/GForm/blob/master/GForm_dist.zip">GForm_dist.zip</a> for the GForm Application, sample scripts,snapshots and help files.

Download the GForm_source.zip for just the gambas basic source code

Happy scripting :)
